Disease:     Dengue
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Dengue virus
Transmission:Aedes mosquito
Symptoms:    Fever, severe joint pain, rash
Treatment:   Supportive care, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.04M
Vaccine:     Yes (for previously infected)
Discovered:  1779

Disease:     Influenza
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Influenza viruses
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, chills, muscle aches
Treatment:   Oseltamivir, rest, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     Yes (annual update)
Discovered:  1933

Disease:     Cancer
Type:        Cellular
Pathogen:    Various causes
Transmission:Non-communicable
Symptoms:    Lumps, weight loss, fatigue
Treatment:   Chemo, surgery, immunotherapy
Deaths/yr:   10.0M
Vaccine:     Some (HPV, Hep B vaccines)
Discovered:  Ancient

